	<AbilityDef  ParentName="RI_PsycastBase" >
		<defName>RI_Activity_LotusPosition</defName>
		<label>Lotus position</label>
		<description>&lt;color=#ED7434&gt;This technique is learned in the Qi Condensation Realm of the Body Refining Method\n\n&lt;/color&gt;Spiritual Energy Consumption: 0.33/second\n\nSitting in lotus position is a basic technique that improves the perception of spiritual energy and meridians in the body by sitting cross-legged. A skilled cultivator can consciously compress the arteries and slow down the blood flow through sitting in lotus position, so that the speed of practice after meditation can be accelerated, and small wounds can automatically recover over time.\n\nThis technique can be turned on and off freely, and spiritual energy will be slowly consumed when it is turned on.</description>
		<iconPath>UI/Abilities/PhysicalStrengthen/RI_Ability_LotusPosition</iconPath>
		<targetRequired>False</targetRequired>
		<canUseAoeToGetTargets>False</canUseAoeToGetTargets>
		<hostile>false</hostile>
		<casterMustBeCapableOfViolence>false</casterMustBeCapableOfViolence>
		<statBases>
			<Ability_Duration>99999</Ability_Duration>
			<Ability_EffectRadius>10</Ability_EffectRadius>
		</statBases>
		<verbProperties>
			<violent>false</violent>
			<warmupTime>0</warmupTime>
			<range>0</range>
			<requireLineOfSight>False</requireLineOfSight>
			<targetParams>
				<canTargetSelf>True</canTargetSelf>
			</targetParams>
		</verbProperties>
		<comps>
			<li Class="CompProperties_AbilityGiveHediff">
				<compClass>CompAbilityEffect_GiveHediff</compClass>
				<hediffDef>RI_LotusPositionHediff</hediffDef>
				<psychic>False</psychic>
				<replaceExisting>False</replaceExisting>
				<onlyApplyToSelf>True</onlyApplyToSelf>
			</li>
			<li Class="WhoXiuXian.Abilities.CompProperties_SpawnMoteCasting">
				<!--选中特效-->
				<moteCastDef>RI_Activity_LotusPosition_Mote</moteCastDef>
				<!--蹦出周天功法几个字-->
			</li>
			<li Class="WhoXiuXian.Abilities.CompProperties_SpawnMoteSinging">
